<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2335] FunctionQParser can&apos;t handle fieldnames containing whitespace</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2335</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FunctionQParser has some simplistic assumptions about what types of field names it will deal with, in particular it can&apos;t deal with field names containing whitespaces.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12496552">SOLR-2335</key>
            <summary>FunctionQParser can&apos;t handle fieldnames containing whitespace</summary>
